            "description": "<p>A gigantic spinal column, ripped whole from a great beast, is posed on the surface of Barrow, enhanced with necromantic technology that turns it into a unliving weapons system. Its skull has been replaced with sensor arrays and deadly ice beam emitters.</p>",
            "disable": "<p>@Check[computers|dc:16] (trained) or @Check[Vidgame Lore|dc:16] (trained) to shut down the necroturret's tech targeting system, @Check[arcana|dc:18] (trained), @Check[nature|dc:18] (trained), @Check[occultism|dc:18] (trained), or @Check[religion|dc:18] (trained) to disrupt the necroturret's magical core, or @Check[athletics|dc:20] or @Check[thievery|dc:20] to destroy vital circuits. A necroturret loses one action from its routine for each successful check made to disable it, or two actions on a critical success.</p>",
            "isComplex": true,
