            "reset": "<p>A necroturret deactivates when it no longer detects living creatures within 120 feet of its location.</p>",
            "routine": "<p>(2 actions) The necroturret uses its actions to attack living creatures with its ice beams. It uses the Lock On reaction once every round to enhance its targeting matrix against the closest living creature. Necroturrets focus on targets trying to disable them.</p>"
